snippet.title: GOOD KILL TEASER
snippet.description:
#Reklam Good Kill is an immersive FPS game where players take control of a door gunner in a military helicopter during the Vietnam War. Engage in intense combat across destructible environments, complete missions, and upgrade your helicopter and weapons to dominate the battlefield.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2705210/Good_Kill/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=good_kill_promotion
Follow us for updates and join our community on Discord: https://discord.gg/uM7QMXY6 #reklam
